### GET
GET http://127.0.0.1:1604/api/books

### POST
POST http://127.0.0.1:1604/api/books
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "author": "Ngo Tat To",
    "title": "Tat Den"
}

### Login get token
# @name login
POST http://127.0.0.1:1604/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "username": "Hoang Ngoc Nhi",
    "password": "0810"
}

### Lưu biến token từ kết quả trả về
@authToken = {{login.response.body.token}}

### GET
GET http://127.0.0.1:1604/api/books
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### POST
POST http://127.0.0.1:1604/api/books
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "author": "Ngo Tat To",
    "title": "Tat Den"
}